OL,3,CWater firms to increase pay outs to
OL,4,Ccustomers affected by supply problems
OL,6,FWater companies will be forced to
OL,7,Fsignificantly increase compensation
OL,8,Fpayments to customers affected by
OL,9,Ffailures such as supply outages, sewer
OL,10,Fflooding or low water pressure, the
OL,11,Fgovernment has said.
OL,13,FCustomers who have problems like low
OL,14,Fwater pressure could receive payments
OL,15,Fof up to #250, compared to the #25
OL,16,Fcurrently available.
