OL,3,CWater firms to increase pay outs to
OL,4,Ccustomers affected by supply problems
OL,6,FThe different circumstances that can
OL,7,Flead to compensation will also include
OL,8,Fwhen Boil Notices are issued because
OL,9,Fof a drop in drinking water quality
OL,10,Fand when firms fail to conduct meter
OL,11,Freadings or installations on time.
OL,13,FThe changes follow a public
OL,14,Fconsultation which found an average of
OL,15,F84% of water customers and 70% of
OL,16,Fbusinesses agreed with the proposals,
OL,17,FDefra said.
