OL,3,CWater firms to increase pay outs to
OL,4,Ccustomers affected by supply problems
OL,6,FThe changes are expected to come into
OL,7,Fforce next year.
OL,9,FSteve Reed, Secretary of State for
OL,10,FEnvironment, Food and Rural Affairs,
OL,11,Fsaid: "Customers have too often been
OL,12,Flet down by water companies, with
OL,13,Fsupply cut off, low water pressure and
OL,14,Fin some cases even contaminated tap
OL,15,Fwater.
OL,17,F"We are clear that the public deserve
OL,18,Fbetter compensation when things go
OL,19,Fwrong, so I'm taking action to make
OL,20,Fsure that happens.
