OL,6,F"This is another step forward in our
OL,7,Fplans to reforms the water sector so
OL,8,Fit serves customers and the
OL,9,Fenvironment better."
OL,11,FPayment rates for firms failing to
OL,12,Fmeet water service standards have
OL,13,Fremained unchanged since 2000.
