OL,3,CWater firms to increase pay outs to
OL,4,Ccustomers affected by supply problems
OL,6,FMike Keil, chief executive of the
OL,7,FConsumer Council for Water (CCW),
OL,8,Fsaid: "The increased payment levels
OL,9,Fwhen things go wrong, alongside fewer
OL,10,Freasons for companies to avoid making
OL,11,Fpayments, means that there are far
OL,12,Fgreater incentives for water companies
OL,13,Fto get things right first time.
OL,15,F"The overhaul of these standards marks
OL,16,Fa step forward in improving consumer
OL,17,Fprotection and repairing fractured
OL,18,Ftrust in the water sector."
